    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 911 Carrera 4S is a mechanically sound example of Porsche\u2019s widebody engineering, powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine. The powerplant delivers linear torque through a G96 six-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system, ensuring optimal power distribution. The chassis features a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, recently enhanced with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal to protect the engine's internal lubrication circuit. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, providing excellent thermal capacity. While the paintwork shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension remain dialed in for performance-oriented driving.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
