    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years\u2014it runs like a dream and still looks fantastic parked in the driveway. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
