    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with a recently serviced dual-mass flywheel. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and upgraded polyurethane bushings to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arms for communicative turn-in and high-speed stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment. A mechanically robust, driver-focused example that balances raw analog feedback with daily usability.",
